7","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b8ce/c158/282351_normal.png?m=1517992357","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b8ce/c158/282351_large.png?m=1517992357","created":1515816918,"last_modified":1517992357},"last_reply_by":"gam2046","last_touched":1649580202,"title":"大家觉得是居家办公工作效率更高，还是去公司更高呢？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846046","created":1649564038,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1649564038,"replies":32,"id":846046},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1635654665","name":"linux","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1635654665","title":"Linux","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","topics":6622,"footer":"","header":"Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.","title_alternative":"Linux","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1635654665","stars":5758,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":11,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":434693,"username":"LittleboyHarry","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LittleboyHarry","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a40/b9bd/434693_mini.png?m=1649557887","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a40/b9bd/434693_normal.png?m=1649557887","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a40/b9bd/434693_large.png?m=1649557887","created":1565312496,"last_modified":1649557887},"last_reply_by":"Tink","last_touched":1649580847,"title":"Arch Linux 图形化简易安装器已被镜像站收录","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846023","created":1649558052,"deleted":0,"content":"昨天收到 [Github 镜像请求通过]( https://github.com/tuna/issues/issues/1466#event-6401872903) 的好消息，\r\n现在 Arch Linux 已被国内镜像站检索、可[极速下载]( https://mirrorz.org/os/ArchLinuxGUI)\r\n\r\n特别感谢 ZenithalHourlyRate 的帮助！\r\n\r\n![截图]( https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/arch-linux-gui/web@master/img/Ss/installer.png)\r\n\r\nArch Linux GUI 旨在提供含有多种可选桌面环境的原版 Arch 系统，\r\n采用了开源的、图形化的 Calamares Linux 安装器 ( 也被如 Manjaro  等发行版采用了 ) \r\n\r\n几乎只需要地区语言、分区、用户信息三步设置即可安装！\r\n甚至可以根据 [Wiki]( https://github.com/calamares/calamares/wiki/Deploy-Configuration) 实现高级自动化、定制化部署\r\n\r\n🙏 愿世上再也没有难以安装的 Arch Linux~","content_rendered":"<p>昨天收到 <a href=\"https://github.com/tuna/issues/issues/1466#event-6401872903\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github 镜像请求通过</a> 的好消息，\n现在 Arch Linux 已被国内镜像站检索、可<a href=\"https://mirrorz.org/os/ArchLinuxGUI\" rel=\"nofollow\">极速下载</a></p>\n<p>特别感谢 ZenithalHourlyRate 的帮助！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"截图\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/arch-linux-gui/web@master/img/Ss/installer.png\"/></p>\n<p>Arch Linux GUI 旨在提供含有多种可选桌面环境的原版 Arch 系统，\n采用了开源的、图形化的 Calamares Linux 安装器 ( 也被如 Manjaro  等发行版采用了 ) </p>\n<p>几乎只需要地区语言、分区、用户信息三步设置即可安装！\n甚至可以根据 <a href=\"https://github.com/calamares/calamares/wiki/Deploy-Configuration\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wiki</a> 实现高级自动化、定制化部署</p>\n<p>🙏 愿世上再也没有难以安装的 Arch Linux~</p>\n","last_modified":1649558052,"replies":28,"id":846023},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1648461133","name":"shenzhen","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1648461133","title":"深圳","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","topics":2361,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Shenzhen","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1648461133","stars":1640,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":21,"parent_node_name":"cn"},"member":{"id":280624,"username":"fs11zhuangb","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fs11zhuangb","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"Talk is cheap, show me the code.\r\n热爱编程，热爱开源。\r\n使用python，C，C++。","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e78a/22a6/280624_mini.png?m=1517908611","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e78a/22a6/280