normal.png?m=1647188067","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":183405,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1647188067","stars":3448,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":19199,"username":"placeless","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/placeless","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02bc/ce14/19199_mini.png?m=1473161850","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02bc/ce14/19199_normal.png?m=1473161850","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02bc/ce14/19199_large.png?m=1473161850","created":1333857917,"last_modified":1473161850},"last_reply_by":"placeless","last_touched":1649583401,"title":"询问：国内简洁好用无需客户端的云盘","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846088","created":1649578577,"deleted":0,"content":"打搅各位，几年前把一部字典移植到了 macOS 内置 Dictionary.app ，一直放在 onedrive ，陆陆续续总有人发信问：\r\n\r\n1. 链接又失效了\r\n2. 下载很慢很慢\r\n3. 有没有百度盘链接\r\n4. 你能不能发给我\r\n\r\n这很尴尬，请教大家，未知 2022 年的当下，国内哪家云盘对用户友好，又不需要我自己操心，还免费（抱歉，没有预算放这上面）。","content_rendered":"<p>打搅各位，几年前把一部字典移植到了 macOS 内置 Dictionary.app ，一直放在 onedrive ，陆陆续续总有人发信问：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>链接又失效了</li>\n<li>下载很慢很慢</li>\n<li>有没有百度盘链接</li>\n<li>你能不能发给我</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这很尴尬，请教大家，未知 2022 年的当下，国内哪家云盘对用户友好，又不需要我自己操心，还免费（抱歉，没有预算放这上面）。</p>\n","last_modified":1649578577,"replies":17,"id":846088},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":18089,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2126,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":264082,"username":"erlking","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/erlking","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a95933c120c86ef43bab59197afdab0?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a95933c120c86ef43bab59197afdab0?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a95933c120c86ef43bab59197afdab0?s=73&d=retro","created":1509505093,"last_modified":1509505093},"last_reply_by":"JVMEXCEPTION","last_touched":1649573202,"title":"HomePod 总是自动连接到非 5g 频段 wifi，大佬们有办法解决吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846025","created":1649558374,"deleted":0,"content":"众所周知 homepod 连非 5g 段很烂，家里 4 台 homepod ，有几台经常自说自话连到 2.4g 频段的 wifi ，太恶心人了。\r\n\r\n试了所有的办法，手机连 5g ，点开 home.app 里的 homepod 显示“切换到同一 wifi 下”属于随机现象，有一台是从来不出现切换的提示的；\r\n试过重启和重置，正常了一段时间又切去 2.4g 了。\r\nwifi 设置里的 2.4g ssid 已经关闭了自动连接，2.4g 频段挂了好多只能设备也不能关，路由器端研究了下，设置里似乎也没有强制绑定设备到频段的选项……\r\n\r\n也不得不吐槽下，都发售这么多年了，连个 wifi 手动切换的功能都不给，真的无语。","content_rendered":"<p>众所周知 homepod 连非 5g 段很烂，家里 4 台 homepod ，有几台经常自说自话连到 2.4g 频段的 wifi ，太恶心人了。</p>\n<p>试了所有的办法，手机连 5g ，点开 home.app 里的 homepod 显示“切换到同一 wifi 下”属于随机现象，有一台是从来不出现切换的提示的；\n试过重启和重置，正常了一段时间又切去 2.4g 了。\nwifi 设置里的 2.4g ssid 已经关闭了自动连接，2.4g 频段挂了好多只能设备也不能关，路由器端研究了下，设置里似乎也没有强制绑定设备到频段的选项……</p>\n<p>也不得不吐槽下，都发售这么多年了，连个 wifi 手动切换的功能都不给，真的无语。</p>\n","last_modified":1649558374,"replies":16,"id":846025},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":10591,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":5497,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":354209,"username":"Zien","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zien","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9153/9772/354209_mini.png?m=1642557720","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9153/9772/354209_normal.png?m=1642557720","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9153/9772/354209_large.png?m=1642557720","created":1538877355,"last_modified":1642557720},"last_reply_by":"sekisui","last_touched":1649561006,"title":"上海的朋友你们最近的宽带和蜂窝网正常吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/845999","created":1649550192,"deleted":0,"content":"我的联通宽带波动比较厉害，尤其是挂代理的设备，但我规则分流没变，而且切换蜂窝网也正常。蜂窝网则是早上六点到八点半抢菜高峰期有波动。是变高了还是只是我的个例？","content_rendered":"我的联通宽带波动比较厉害，尤其是挂代理的设备，但我规则分流没变，而且切换蜂窝网也正常。蜂窝网则是早上六点到八点半抢菜高峰期有波动。是变高了还是只是我的个例？","last_modified":1649550192,"replies":16,"id":845999},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":10591,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":5497,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":558213,"username":"viberconnection","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/viberconnection","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dbb98ba5be1d13ea8b83daa6c233b778?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dbb98ba5be1d13ea8b83daa6c233b778?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dbb98ba5be1d13ea8b83daa6c233b778?s=73&d=retro","created":1633993018,"last_modified":1639313018},"last_reply_by":"aheadlead","last_touched":1649570623,"title":"被福建電信給氣壞了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846020","created":1649556976,"deleted":0,"content":"由於自己在大陸的住處範圍內僅存有電信的寬帶資源，所以剛到的時候，我就安裝了電信的寬帶。\r\n剛開始用的還正常，但隨著眾所周知的原因，近期卻變得不正常起來。簡單來說現象就是這樣子。\r\n\r\n1.當去各類網路存儲服務下載文件超過 100G ，相關服務的連結速度就會變得十分緩慢。\r\n2.相關程式總連結時長超過一定時數後，UDP 開始隨機丟包，導致視訊會議都無法正常進行。\r\n3.NAT type 會在 Fullcone 和 Symmetric 之間不斷循環，然後每隔幾個小時網路就會 Hang 一下數秒。\r\n4.上行速率不穩定。\r\n\r\n這段時間都快被煩透了。然後除了電信提供的 Modem 無法排查以外，其他自己的網路設備找不出任何問題。。。\r\n所以真的很好奇這種問題為何會發生，或者是說是時候該更換 ISP 了嗎。","content_rendered":"由於自己在大陸的住處範圍內僅存有電信的寬帶資源，所以剛到的時候，我就安裝了電信的寬帶。<br />剛開始用的還正常，但隨著眾所周知的原因，近期卻變得不正常起來。簡單來說現象就是這樣子。<br /><br />1.當去各類網路存儲服務下載文件超過 100G ，相關服務的連結速度就會變得十分緩慢。<br />2.相關程式總連結時長超過一定時數後，UDP 開始隨機丟包，導致視訊會議都無法正常進行。<br />3.NAT type 會在 Fullcone 和 Symmetric 之間不斷循環，然後每隔幾個小時網路就會 Hang 一下數秒。<br />4.上行速率不穩定。<br /><br />這段時間都快被煩透了。然後除了電信提供的 Modem 無法排查以外，其他自己的網路設備找不出任何問題。。。<br />所以真的很好奇這種問題為何會發生，或者是說是時候該更換 ISP 了嗎。","last_modified":1649556976,"replies":15,"id":846020},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1649311216","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1649311216","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":48201,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1649311216","stars":7768,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":216901,"username":"DiamondYuan","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DiamondYuan","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d8175c2ed4ddb8f35a2d3796f3fbf9?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d8175c2ed4ddb8f35a2d3796f3fbf9?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d8175c2ed4ddb8f35a2d3796f3fbf9?s=73&d=retro","created":1487838472,"last_modified":1648471537},"