Chan","last_touched":1649575450,"title":"有个奇葩的需求，服务器怎么整个声卡","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846063","created":1649569166,"deleted":0,"content":"现在有个奇葩的需求，在服务器上需要录制一些视频，但是众所周知服务器是没有声卡的（ Windows Server 默认也会关闭音频服务），因为服务器本身是没有音频相关硬件的，请问大家有什么好主意能内录到音频吗？\r\n\r\n - 该视频无法从源头下载，只能录制\r\n \r\n - 我无法更改该服务器的任何硬件\r\n \r\n我的设想是用一个类似于虚拟声卡的软件模拟出来一个音频硬件，反正也无法输出，只需要 bandicam 能接收就可以","content_rendered":"<p>现在有个奇葩的需求，在服务器上需要录制一些视频，但是众所周知服务器是没有声卡的（ Windows Server 默认也会关闭音频服务），因为服务器本身是没有音频相关硬件的，请问大家有什么好主意能内录到音频吗？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>该视频无法从源头下载，只能录制</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>我无法更改该服务器的任何硬件</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>我的设想是用一个类似于虚拟声卡的软件模拟出来一个音频硬件，反正也无法输出，只需要 bandicam 能接收就可以</p>\n","last_modified":1649569166,"replies":10,"id":846063},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598","name":"macos","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598","title":"macOS","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","topics":18257,"footer":"<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。","header":"The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.","title_alternative":"macOS","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598","stars":4586,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":22,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":500658,"username":"kyro00000","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kyro00000","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc70/20b5/500658_mini.png?m=1641541354","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc70/20b5/500658_normal.png?m=1641541354","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc70/20b5/500658_large.png?m=1641541354","created":1595595758,"last_modified":1641541354},"last_reply_by":"pythonnoob","last_touched":1649563792,"title":"m1book 和黑苹果 可以兼用 4k144 显示器？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846002","created":16